ust manage the sensors attached to it" satisfied by SMSComponents.SensorMicrocontrollerCP ; } Requirement AutoUploadFR ( 1.4.1 ) { text = "Automatic collected data via HUB" satisfied by SMSComponents.HubCP ; } Requirement RealTimeTransmissionFR ( 1.4.2 ) { text = "Totem should transmit real-time data to the system" satisfied by SMSComponents.TotemCP ; } Requirement MicrocontrollerDataSendFR ( 1.4.3 ) { text = "Microcontroller should send recorded data to the system" satisfied by SMSComponents.SensorMicrocontrollerCP ; } Requirement TotemAuthenticationFR ( 1.5.1 ) { text = "Totem allows training session start through QR Core/RFID authentication" satisfied by SMSComponents.TotemCP ; } Requirement TotemEndTrainingFR ( 1.5.2 ) { text = "Totem must allow athlete to finish training session" satisfied by SMSComponents.TotemCP ; } Requirement MultiStartOptionFR ( 1.5.3 ) { text = "The athlete may start training session via totem or mobile" satisfied by SMSComponents.TotemCP ; } Requirement DisplayAthleteDataFR ( 1.6.1 ) { text = "The system must display anthlete name on scoreboard" satisfied by SMSComponents.ElectronicScoreboardCP ; } Requirement DisplayTimingFR ( 1.6.2 ) { text = "Teh system must display athlete time data (Session Elapsed Time, Current Lap Time)" satisfied by SMSComponents.ElectronicScoreboardCP ; } Requirement ScoreboardUpdateFR ( 1.6.3 ) { text = "The scoreboard must be updated in real-time" satisfied by SMSComponents.ElectronicScoreboardCP ; } Requirement CaptureMovementFR ( 1.7.1 ) { text = "Cameras must capture movement in pool lanes" satisfied by SMSComponents.CameraCP ; } Requirement VideoStreamingFR ( 1.7.2 ) { text = "The system must allow video streaming/recording" satisfied by SMSComponents.CameraCP ; } Requirement BackupDetectionFR ( 1.7.3 ) { text = "The system must provide video analysis as sensor failover" satisfied by SMSComponents.CameraCP ; } Requirement GenerateReportsFR ( 1.8.1 ) { text = "The system must generate individual performance